@startuml
!theme plain
title Consistency Problem: Delete Cache First, then Update DB

actor "Request A (Write)" as A
actor "Request B (Read)" as B
entity "Cache" as Cache
database "Database" as DB

A -> Cache : Delete cache
B -> Cache : Cache miss
B -> DB : Read old value from DB (value = 20)
B -> Cache : Update cache with old value (update to 20)
A -> DB : Update DB with new value (update to 21)

note over A, DB #LightPink
**Result: DB = 21, Cache = 20 -> Data inconsistency**
end note

@enduml